    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
