    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule: this vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, indistinguishable from the day it left the factory. The Deep Pearl Black exterior retains a mirror-like finish, free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are firm and show zero signs of bolstering wear or creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. All high-gloss trim pieces are scratch-free, and every electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained strictly by authorized technicians. The engine bay is concours-clean, and the undercarriage reflects the same level of obsessive care. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved investment for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
